      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "VAEDecode 把高级采样器输出的 LATENT 还原成 IMAGE。它本身不需要下载额外文件，所需模型来自 VAELoader。\n\n若出现花屏、偏色或解码失败，检查 samples、vae 两条输入线，并确认 VAE 选择 ae.safetensors。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
    {
      "id": 89,
      "type": "Note",
      "pos": [
        1854.8331298828125,
        671.9760131835938
