      "properties": {
        "widget_ue_connectable": {},
        "text": ""
      },
      "widgets_values": [
        "FLUX 同时使用 T5-XXL 和 CLIP-L 理解提示词。当前 T5 使用 FP8，显存占用更低；类型保持 flux，device 通常保持 default。\n\nT5 文件：t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/t5xxl_fp8_e4m3fn.safetensors?download=true\n\nCLIP 文件：clip_l.safetensors\n下载：https://huggingface.co/comfyanonymous/flux_text_encoders/resolve/main/clip_l.safetensors?download=true\n\n存放：D:\\ComfyUI\\models\\text_encoders\n下载后刷新模型列表并选择同名文件。"
      ],
      "color": "#223",
      "bgcolor": "#335"
    },
