        "An anime-style illustration inspired by Studio Ghibli, featuring a spirited young protagonist named KAKA, wearing a flowing white dress and a wide-brimmed straw hat, riding on the back of a large friendly forest spirit that resembles a gentle wolf. In her right hand, she cheerfully holds up a rustic wooden sign, with the name \"KAKA\" painted on it in bright, playful rainbow-colored letters. They are leaping over a crystal-clear stream deep inside a lush green valley during early summer. Sunlight filters through the leaves, casting soft bokeh effects all around. Wildflowers in shades of lavender and yellow blanket the meadows. The background showcases rolling green hills and a quaint little windmill in the distance. The composition is open and airy, with a strong emphasis on nature and tranquility. KAKA's hair and dress are dynamically flowing in the wind, the sign also swaying slightly, conveying a sense of freedom and joy. Soft pastel gradients, cel-shaded yet with painterly textures, serene and poetic visual narrative.\n"
